ACTIVITY #2
vim is basically a editor like notepad. Here Vim  editor is used for coding.there are some shorcut keys through which we can edit vim file.
some of them are given below
gg  move to first line
G   move to last line
nG  move to n'th line of file (where n is a number) 

Vim has configration file named .vimrc .This file contains all the startup configrations of vim editor. you can make custom thoeo configrations for your vim editor.
An image of my .vimrc file is also attacked with it 
